high_descs: Walk up to the right side of the sink counter.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the toilet tank to your right.
Walk over to the rightmost sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk towards the shower, turn left again to face the counter.
Open the second cabinet door from the right below the counter and put the clean bar of soap inside, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in a cabinet.

high_descs: Pick up the soap on the toilet.
Bring the soap to the right sink.
Wash the soap in the right sink.
Bring the washed soap to the cabinet under the right sink.
Put the washed soap in the left cabinet under the right sink.
anns.task_desc: Put washed soap away in a cabinet.

high_descs: Walk forward to the sink counter
Pick up the soap on the right side of sink counter
Turn left then face the sink
Put the soap in the sink and rinse it
Turn around to your right then move a little
Open the cabinet on your left and put it the soap
anns.task_desc: Put the clean soap in the cabinet
